resources.string:
This application is used for data collection of passive sensing of mental health study by UCLA ER (eHealth Research) Lab and MITRE. 

Our goals with this initial data collection effort are two-fold: 

 1. To build a proof-of-concept technology platform capable of collecting, storing, and analyzing measures. 
 2. Determining which metrics best correlate to which measures of mental health.
Please, get in touch with us to report any issues or recommendations about the app.
Instruction: When you want to complete the daily survey, press the START button to view the questionnaire.
